                                                                                            <p><strong>Owshnik Ghosh</strong> is a Bengali writer. His first book of poetry was published in 2024. Besides poetry, he is also an essayist and a translator. He has done a master’s degree in comparative Indian language and literature from the University of Calcutta and at present is pursuing his PhD from the University of Oklahoma. His research interest is in South Asian literature and culture.</p>
